You can get help at almost every button, menuitem
or component in DigSim.

To get help about something is very simple:

1) Choose 'help' in the menu bar.

2) Choose a menu, button or component
in the schematic to get help about
that object.

When choosing a digital component in the schematic,
you get the following information about the
selected electronic component:

* A general description.
* The truth-table.
* Editing capabilities.
